Notts County have appointed Ricardo Moniz as their new manager on a three-year deal . 
  The former Tottenham and Hamburg coach pulled out of the running due to 'family reasons' Moniz has six games to save Notts County from relegation to League Two . 
  The Magpies are currently one point from safety . 
  Dave Kevan will be Moniz's assistant at Meadow Lane . 
 